@startuml sequence-data-kucing
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Kelola Data Kucing

actor Pelanggan
participant "Aplikasi Web" as App
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

== Tambah Kucing ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka menu "Kucing Saya"
Pelanggan -> App : Isi form kucing\n+ riwayat vaksin (opsional)
App -> API : POST /kucing
API -> API : Validasi input
API -> DB : BEGIN TRANSACTION
API -> DB : INSERT kucing (pelanggan_id)
DB --> API : kucing_id
opt Ada riwayat vaksin
  API -> DB : INSERT riwayat_vaksin (batch)
end
API -> DB : COMMIT
DB --> API : OK
API --> App : 201 Created
App --> Pelanggan : Kucing berhasil ditambahkan

== Edit Kucing ==

Pelanggan -> App : Pilih kucing & edit data
App -> API : PUT /kucing/{id}
API -> DB : SELECT kucing WHERE id & pelanggan_id
alt Bukan milik pelanggan login
  API --> App : 403 Forbidden
else Milik pelanggan
  API -> DB : UPDATE kucing + riwayat_vaksin
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : 200 OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Data kucing diperbarui
end

== Hapus Kucing ==

Pelanggan -> App : Pilih kucing & hapus
App -> API : DELETE /kucing/{id}
API -> DB : Cek booking aktif pada kucing
alt Masih ada booking aktif
  DB --> API : Booking aktif ditemukan
  API --> App : 409 Conflict
  App --> Pelanggan : Penghapusan ditolak
else Tidak ada booking aktif
  API -> DB : DELETE kucing (CASCADE riwayat_vaksin)
  DB --> API : OK
  API --> App : 200 OK
  App --> Pelanggan : Kucing berhasil dihapus
end

== Lihat Daftar ==

Pelanggan -> App : Buka "Kucing Saya"
App -> API : GET /kucing
API -> DB : SELECT kucing + riwayat_vaksin\nWHERE pelanggan_id
DB --> API : Daftar kucing
API --> App : 200 OK + data
App --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan daftar kucing

@enduml
